## Limitations

The analysis is based on a limited number of sources, which may not capture the full spectrum of opinions and research on the topic. Additionally, the data is current only up to October 2023, and newer developments or studies may not be included. The perspectives presented are primarily from U.S.-based sources, which may not reflect global views on college affordability.